{"type": "article", "id": 31562, "title": "年轻人最爱苹果，以及，H&M 发布 2016 秋冬潮流趋势 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-08-29T02:32:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 188, "name": "LV"}, {"id": 1936, "name": "香水"}, {"id": 231, "name": "Apple"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 17867, "name": "Herschel Supply"}, {"id": 32104, "name": "E.l.f. Cosmetics"}, {"id": 32105, "name": "Ultra Beauty"}, {"id": 3264, "name": "山本耀司"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160829095042jNvOkhxAgMJomSd5.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/marketing-consumer-behavior/millennial-brand-ranking-apple-still-tops-chart-fast-fashion-dips-10515821/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Apple 依然是千禧一代最喜欢的品牌</b></a> | 数字代理公司<a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/marketing-consumer-behavior/millennial-brand-ranking-apple-still-tops-chart-fast-fashion-dips-10515821/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> </a>Moosylvania 发布了最新的千禧一代最喜欢的品牌排行榜。其中，Apple 继续蝉联第一，Nike，Target，Sony 以及可口可乐位列前五。<br></p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/prada-profits-slump-25-in-h1-sales-falter-10515689/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Prada 2016 上半年业绩低迷</b></a> | 据 Prada 的报告称，受糟糕的全球外贸市场影响，该公司在 2016 年上半年净利润下跌 25%，至 1.419 亿欧元。总的营收下跌了 15%，至 15.54 亿欧元。Prada 将采取成本削减计划，以保持利润。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/financial/e-l-f-cosmetics-files-ipo-plans-expansion-10516367/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国平价彩妆品牌 E.l.f. Cosmetics 寻求上市</b></a> | 上周五， E.l.f. Cosmetics 公布了它的上市计划。该品牌创立于 2004 年，是一个主打“快时尚”的平价彩妆品牌，主要的销售渠道是美国的各大超市。E.l.f. Cosmetics 在 2016 上半年的销售额为 9680 万美元，净收入为 110 万美元。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/fragrance/louis-vuitton-parfums-five-pop-ups-for-perfume-launch-10515811/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>LV 要开香水快闪店</b></a> | 为了给新推出的香水产品造势，Louis Vuitton 计划在全球范围内开设快闪店。首批的五家店分别位于巴黎、伦敦、迪拜和首尔。店铺持续时间约为两个月。&nbsp;</p><p><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/financial/mass-prestige-color-cosmetics-drive-ulta-sales-gains-10515538/\" rel=\"nofollow\">美国著名美容产品连锁店 Ultra Beauty 第二季度收入大涨</a> </b>| 由于彩妆系列的销量持续增长，Ultra Beauty 在第二季度净收入上涨了 21.3%，至 9000 万美元，销售额上涨了 21.9%，至 10.7 亿美元。Ultra Beauty 在第二季度新开了 24 家店，它的会员人数达到了 2060 万。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>美国时尚品牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/opening-ceremony-2016-fall-winter-the-warmup\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Opening Ceremony 发布 The Warm Up 秋冬系列特辑</a>。该系列兼具了实穿性和功能性，提供了一套从健身房到办公室的完美着装解决方案。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829095216goECzdF7K84PAsTH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829095216PKQEBjH5WVgMmLGC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667002\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829095222gltmU2TnjBrQ4iNb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829095231iYPhgbQ7cMN5zkaU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Adidas <a href=\"http://popbee.com/accessories/shoes/barricade-adicolor/#\" rel=\"nofollow\">推出 Barricade adicolor D.I.Y. 定制套装系列</a>。这一套装内包括一双小白鞋，以及红、黄、绿、橙、蓝、黑六种颜色笔，还有五色鞋带。可以发挥创意，绘制出一双独一无二的鞋子。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829095246yKk2obgXMt5qSW7h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829095246TW1qyfCcHG26VIkm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829095246jKcpCx1vlIiW5RXP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829095252fhkvEsKCWiZ1bwT2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>山本耀司旗下支线品牌  <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/ys-by-yohji-yamamoto-new-era-2016-capsule\" rel=\"nofollow\">Y’s by Yoshi Yamamoto 与美国制帽商 New Era 再度合作</a>，推出了针织帽以及皮草飞行帽系列，此外，该系列中的皮革拼接的羊毛棒球夹克也还不错。这个联名系列已经登陆  Y’s by Yoshi Yamamoto 日本各大门店，售价为 7500 到 78000 日元不等。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829095301BPqnrQo5KYClxOIF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829095301Fhrn1NkupXzlE4wW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829095311VdUqigWIRu4Grosf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608290953117XhzrwRTD49iAJMO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668281\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829095311D6j5RqNxFShEa83m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667051\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/fall-2016-outfits-hm-lookbook/\" rel=\"nofollow\">H&amp;M 发布了 2016 秋冬潮流趋势，</a>以 The New Eclectic “新的折衷主义”为主题，推出了毛衫、蕾丝裙、短夹克等系列产品。由模特 Rianne van Rompaey 进行演绎。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">&nbsp;<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829095334hN4PoazWlDup9LnH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829095334QsDEqozpJludbRK5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016082909533474KWduDAISh8r5Pw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829095334UuOKfcEwal0RJrZx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829095343D5eMm2xUonbpEilj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829095343DVmrgLcYaTk9fQtx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>加拿大箱包品牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/herschel-supply-gore-tex-headwear-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Herschel Supply 与 GORE-TEX 联名推出帽款系列</a>，主打日常和户外风格，结合了 GORE-TEX 的机能性和 Herschel Supply 的设计感。目前已经登录全球各大指定店铺及品牌的官方网站。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829095354C1cQHJLi3bABU2q4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829095409ltGPMS7wkFTVa849.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829095409sbYhiI30GxZ65JPA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829095409VBtb6Rs1cfPJKhLg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}